{"tid":212210,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 黑椒牛仔骨炒飯底","createTime":"2017-04-22T08:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T05:43:52.000Z","uid":74981,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b99101feae587f2362d59dcc7dd90941db62610","tid":212210,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c2a77e7f5b0d012eee01588b00865fc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc2a77e7f5b0d012eee01588b00865fc9.jpg&h=62f477f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/af82f7cd198c5642f0b446e39b8dd593.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Faf82f7cd198c5642f0b446e39b8dd593.jpg&h=6d115971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片如下:<br />\n<br />\nPART 1(醃牛仔骨同炒飯底)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uYU8a_OC3tY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuYU8a_OC3tY&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e79d3bb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uYU8a_OC3tY</a><br />\n<br />\nPART 2 (黑椒牛仔骨)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w5tsczBuALE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw5tsczBuALE&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1048e0c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w5tsczBuALE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n材料:<br />\n<br />\n1. 牛仔骨2塊解凍切成6舊<br />\n<br />\n2. 1隻蛋炒1乜新鮮飯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛仔骨用以下醃料醃15分鐘:<br />\n<br />\n1. 生抽1.5茶匙<br />\n<br />\n2. 美極1.5茶匙<br />\n<br />\n3. 糖大半茶匙<br />\n<br />\n4. 黑胡椒粒2茶匙打碎<br />\n<br />\n5. 生粉1茶匙加1茶匙水開勻<br />\n<br />\n6. 油2.5茶匙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑椒汁材料:<br />\n<br />\n1. 洋蔥半個<br />\n<br />\n2. 蒜蓉1茶匙<br />\n<br />\n3. 黑胡椒碎 (可加可不加, 因為本癲狗已經用左大量黑胡碎醃過D牛仔骨再拎去煎, 所以個獲D油已經有煎香過既黑胡椒味, 唔洗洗獲用番D油炒洋蔥去煮個汁, 就算唔再加黑胡椒, 都已經夠黑胡椒味. 當然, 你想重D黑胡椒味, 咁再加D黑胡椒碎煮個汁亦無妨.<br />\n<br />\n4. 大半碗水<br />\n<br />\n5. 新鮮辣椒1條切碎<br />\n<br />\n6. 鹽半茶匙<br />\n<br />\n7. 糖大半茶匙<br />\n<br />\n8. 美極1湯匙<br />\n<br />\n9. 李派林GAP汁1茶匙<br />\n<br />\n10. 茄汁1茶匙<br />\n<br />\n11. 老抽半茶匙<br />\n<br />\n12. 生粉1茶匙加1茶匙水開勻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做法概述:<br />\n<br />\n1. 炒飯底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/996b13b16bcbce61e660ceca66726d88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F996b13b16bcbce61e660ceca66726d88.jpg&h=6d6fba30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 獲燒紅落油, 大火煎牛仔骨每邊10幾20秒<br />\n<br />\n3. 反一反, 用中細火煎每邊分幾兩分鐘, 目的係要全熟. 哩D街市雪藏牛仔骨全熟穩陣D, 而且全熟都唔會唔好食.<br />\n<br />\n3. 撈起牛仔骨, 用番D油開中火炒洋蔥, 如太多油就倒走少少.<br />\n<br />\n4. 洋蔥炒至香, 落蒜蓉1茶匙和黑胡椒碎 (可加可不加, 黑椒汁材料個LIST有解釋到) 轉細火略炒香, 加水大半碗, 煮滾收細火.<br />\n<br />\n5. 落齊以上黑椒汁材料 (5至12點), 熄火, 倒番D牛仔骨落D汁到略炒.<br />\n<br />\n6.將牛仔骨連汁鋪上炒飯面, 完成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68de72a8d775e403971c1e29d9a620eef83f7dd0","tid":212210,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8117af64588b525388ee95c0cf0badd681e1a7b8","tid":212210,"uid":51108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"嘩正喎!"},{"pid":"47226369646df7f940d5f60ffee3c207ea561f0a","tid":212210,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n弘b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340f8afd6839ea23ceef108e3b9d6cc135f178df","tid":212210,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩正喎!</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738f67703377ddf71e2a0757512df6eecfa361bb","tid":212210,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:15:45.000Z